data.description:
Welcome to this charming 1900's 3-bedroom, 2.5 bath home nestled on a corner lot in the heart of Faribault. Featuring large bedrooms, formal & informal dining, with an open concept that just flows into the kitchen. Enjoy close proximity to shopping, schools and parks, and easy access to major highways and interstate 35.
The basement offers a large family/game room, as well as a large cold storage room and lots of EXTRA space, 1/2 bath and laundry.
Be sure to check out this property before it gone.
